notes:
15-Aug-2024 tlinack (SC) - Update of specification for commercial purpose as per ETS 2365185

-PARTICULATE MATTER 7 (v1) 1LIST

-IC A280 SAMPLE (v1) 6N 4NC
-PH20 ACTIVITY (v1) 1N

-CSDS NON-REDUCED (v1) 1N 1LIST 2
-PEPTIDE MAPPING 1 (v1) 5N
